WorkItem.Description:
If you have an __autoload function defined, then you may get the following error message when trying to create PDF output using PHPExcel_Writer_PDF
 
Warning: require_once(FPDF.php) [function.require-once]: failed to open stream: No such file or directory in /var/www/localhost/htdocs/_phpexcel/index.php on line 8
 
Fatal error: require_once() [function.require]: Failed opening required 'FPDF.php' (include_path='.:/usr/share/php5:/usr/share/php:/var/www/localhost/htdocs/_phpexcel/PHPExcel/Classes/:/var/www/localhost/htdocs/_phpexcel/Extras/') in /var/www/localhost/htdocs/_phpexcel/index.php on line 8
